ded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full-time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - which has been vital on their pathway to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.04990491936607e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"benefit\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"their pathway\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teenager began to turn heads with her performances in 2023, becoming England Under-20 and English Schools inter girls 800m champion and clocking some impressive times.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_under-20_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9686608850325664, \"rank\": 0.03235303030366259, \"text\": \"England Under-20\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_under-20_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_under-20_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\", \"score\": 0.6569967524716824, \"rank\": 0.2819030639905543, \"text\": \"English\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The teenager\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"her performances\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"m champion\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"some impressive times\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That led her to the Commonwealth Youth Games in Trinidad and Tobago where she won gold and broke Jessica Ennis-Hill's championship record.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Youth_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.843512859691454e-12, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Youth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Youth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Youth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"score\": 0.9896023776443931, \"rank\": 0.010506034194554002, \"text\": \"Trinidad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\"}, {\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tobago\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gill is far from a tourist at these Games and will hope to be in the mix for bronze, with teammate Hodgkinson and Kenya's Mary Moraa expected to duke it out for gold and silver.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.916842934894318, \"rank\": 0.09069935748053769, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999704846236, \"rank\": 2.2642072650964522e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.8540286391053412, \"rank\": 0.15375625135138662, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"a tourist\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's easy to say I am coming in with no expectations, but I think every athlete always puts some goals in their head,\\\" Gill said.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no expectations\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"every athlete\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"some goals\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"their head\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's just to progress through as many rounds as possible and to have run and run with freedom the entire time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as many rounds\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The St Albans native does not have far to look when it comes to an example of how to stay grounded amid a rapid early rise to the top.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The St Albans\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"a rapid early rise\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daleyhas been chosen to carry the Great Britain flag in the Opening Ceremony on the River Seine, 16 years since stepping on the Olympic stage as a 14-year-old.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2458, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 2.9038761842471467e-12, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom Daleyhas\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"the River Seine\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am grateful to be going to the Games at this age because I know there is less pressure on me now,\\\" Gill said.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"this age\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"less pressure\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"Gill\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ever since I ran 1:57, I have felt older in a way and started to compare myself to more mature athletes.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"more mature athletes\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think that was the best thing to do because you draw higher expectations just because you have run fast.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"higher expectations\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I sometimes need to remind myself and ground myself that I am still a teenager and do have a long career left.\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"a long career\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's weird seeing people compare me to Tom Daley and other young Olympians.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.573857953997924e-41, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"other young Olympians\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope I have successful journeys like them.\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"successful journeys\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember watching them when I was younger and thinking they were such inspiring people.\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such inspiring people\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully I can be like them and a role model on my journey in athletics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a role model\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3296}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With more than \\u00a330m a week raised for good causes, including vital funding into elite and grassroots sport, National Lottery players support our Olympic and Paralympic athletes to live their dreams and make the nation proud, as well as providing more opportunities for people to take part in sport.\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3435, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999977525833644, \"rank\": 2.2474202940536015e-06, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than \\u00a330m\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"good causes\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"vital funding\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"elite and